<h3>Why This Could Work</h3>
<ol>
<li><strong>Bottom-up adoption</strong>: Unlike Workday (forced top-down), this spreads because PIs love it and tell other PIs</li>
<li><strong>No institutional buy-in required initially</strong>: A PI can start with just a CSV of their grants</li>
<li><strong>Foundation funding potential</strong>: Aligns with Wellcome, Gates, NIH goals for global research capacity</li>
<li><strong>Open source wedge</strong>: <a href="https://www.quora.com/What-are-the-best-open-source-grants-management-software">CiviCRM model</a> shows this can work for nonprofits</li>
<li><strong>Mobile-first for global reach</strong>: Works on a $200 smartphone in rural settings</li>
