     Want to upload the proposal so I can remember 
     what you committed to?&quot;
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Total time: 60 seconds. No Workday codes. No account numbers.</strong></p>
<hr />
<h3>How AI Adds Value</h3>
<p>The AI isn't generating grants. It's:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Extracting structure</strong> from uploaded proposals (aims, budget, timeline)</li>
<li><strong>Answering questions</strong> against your data ("Can I hire...?")</li>
<li><strong>Remembering commitments</strong> ("What did I promise in Year 2?")</li>
<li><strong>Searching across grants</strong> ("Which grant could fund phage work?")</li>
<li><strong>Projecting forward</strong> ("When will I run out at current pace?")</li>
</ol>
<hr />
<h3>What This Means for MVP</h3>
<p><strong>Phase 1: Grant Portfolio</strong>
- Add grants (conversationally, simple fields)
